 stats_update         = april 8th, 2020\n| extra_information    = \n}}\n'''Ryan Adams''' (born May 14, 1991), known professionally as '''Ryland Adams''', is an American [[YouTuber]], Internet personality, writer, producer, and actor. In 2014, Adams became an on-air host and producer for [[ClevverTV|Clevver]], an online pop culture media company. Adams later left Clevver in 2017, citing questionable business practices.<ref>{{cite web |title=Exposing a Youtube Company |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SclwwbDynUI |website=YouTube |last=Adams|first=Ryland}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Jarvey |first1=Natalie |title=A Class-Action Lawsuit, Late Creator Payments: Inside Defy Media's Shutdown |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/defy-medias-shutdown-provokes-class-action-lawsuit-complaints-late-creator-payments-1160929 |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=February 21, 2019}}</ref> Adams entered into a relationship with fellow YouTuber [[Shane Dawson]] in 2016, and is primarily known for his [[Vlog|YouTube vlogs]] about his life. As of February 2019, his videos have received an average of 3.8 million views.<ref>{{cite web |title=ryanadams7 YouTube Stats, Channel Statistics - Socialblade.com |url=https://socialblade.com/youtube/user/ryanadams7 |publisher=Social Blade |accessdate=February 21, 2019}}</ref>\n\nIn 2019, Adams received the [[Shorty Awards|Shorty Award]] for Vlogger of the Year.<ref>{{cite web |title=Ryland Adams \u2013 Vlogger of the Year \u2013 The Shorty Awards |url=https://shortyawards.com/11th/ryland_adams |publisher=The Shorty Awards |accessdate=February 21, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://metro.co.uk/2019/05/06/shane-dawson-wins-youtuber-year-shorty-awards-no-one-handling-9417474/|title=YouTuber Shane Dawson wins at Shorty Awards and no one is handling it|date=2019-05-06|website=Metro|access-date=2019-05-06}}</ref>\n\nShane Dawson and Ryland Adams have been a YouTube favourite couple since 2016 when they first got together and luckily for the YouTube community the dynamic duo became engaged in March 2019 on a moonlit cliff hanging over the ocean, Ryland thought that they were just doing a photo shoot on the pier but when Shane pulled out the ring it made Ryland the happiest man of the year.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.eonline.com/uk/news/1025109/youtube-star-shane-dawson-is-engaged-to-ryland-adams-see-the-proposal-photos|title=YouTube Star Shane Dawson Is Engaged to Ryland Adams: See the Proposal Photos|date=March 20, 2019|website=E! News|accessdate=2019-11-26}}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n===Web===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 2013\u20132017\n| ''Clevver News''\n| rowspan=\"7\" | Himself\n| Main role\n|-\n| 2015\u20132016\n| ''Throwback''\n| Main role\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2018\n| ''The Truth About Tanacon''\n| 1 episode\n|-\n| ''[[The Secret World of Jeffree Star]]''\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[The Mind of Jake Paul]]''\n| 3 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2019\n| ''[[Conspiracy Series with Shane Dawson]]''\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[The Beautiful World of Jeffree Star]]''\n| 7 episodes \n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Notes\n! Result\n|-\n|2019\n|[[The Shorty Awards]]\n|Vlogger of the Year<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2019-shorty-award-winners-list-full-1206922/item/actor-shorty-winners-2019-1207056|title=Actor \u2013 Michelle Obama, Noah Centineo, Marie Kondo, John Mulaney Win 2019 Shorty Awards|website=The Hollywood Reporter|language=en|access-date=2019-05-06}}</ref>\n|\n|{{won}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{official website|http://www.rylandadams.com/}}\n* {{IMDb name|4084314}}\n* {{Youtube|u=ryanadams7|Ryland Adams}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Adams, Ryland}}\n[[Category:American YouTubers]]\n[[Category:Gay actors]]\n[[Category:Gay writers]]\n[[Category:LGBT people from California]]\n[[Categor