ng\">{{cite web |title=Best of All Time: Albums |publisher=Hung Medien |url=http://norwegiancharts.com/bestall_a.asp |work=[[VG-lista]] |accessdate=June 22, 2012 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120109172856/http://norwegiancharts.com/bestall_a.asp |archivedate=January 9, 2012 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"iht\">{{cite news|last=Purdum |first=Todd |title=The Sound of Music:40 years of unstoppable success |newspaper=International Herald Tribune |date=June 1, 2005 |url=http://www.iht.com/articles/2005/05/31/features/music.php |accessdate=January 18, 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050602003450/http://www.iht.com/articles/2005/05/31/features/music.php |archivedate=June 2, 2005 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"latimes-boehm\">{{cite news |last=Boehm |first=Mike |title=Howard Terpning's paintings keep Old West alive |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |date=May 17, 2012 |url=https://articles.latimes.com/2012/may/17/entertainment/la-ca-howard-terpning-20120520 |accessdate=March 15, 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20150316155413/http://articles.latimes.com/2012/may/17/entertainment/la-ca-howard-terpning-20120520 |archivedate=March 16, 2015 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"mojo-tickets\">{{cite web |title=The Sound of Music: Domestic Grosses |publisher=Box Office Mojo |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/adjusted.htm?adjust_yr=1 |accessdate=March 22, 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402130846/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/adjusted.htm?adjust_yr=1 |archivedate=April 2, 2015 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"numbers\">{{cite web |title=The Sound of Music |publisher=The Numbers |url=https://www.the-numbers.com/movies/1965/0SOMU.php |accessdate=April 26, 2011 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110903150430/http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/1965/0SOMU.php |archivedate=September 3, 2011 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"numbers-index\">{{cite web |title=Movie Index |publisher=The Numbers |url=https://www.the-numbers.com/movies/#tab=year |accessdate=March 22, 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150316153502/http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/#tab=year |archivedate=March 16, 2015 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"nytimes-awards\">{{cite news|title=The Sound of Music (1965): Awards |newspaper=The New York Times |url=https://www.nytimes.com/movies/movie/45745/The-Sound-of-Music/awards |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150210055029/https://www.nytimes.com/movies/movie/45745/The-Sound-of-Music/awards |archivedate=February 10, 2015}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"nytimes-barthel\">{{cite news |last=Barthel |first=Joan |title=The Sound of Music: Biggest Money-Making Movie of All Time |newspaper=The New York Times |date=November 20, 1966 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/packages/html/movies/bestpictures/music-ar.html |accessdate=March 22, 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305090728/http://www.nytimes.com/packages/html/movies/bestpictures/music-ar.html |archivedate=March 5, 2016 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"nytimes-crowther\">{{cite news |last=Crowther |first=Bosley |title=The Sound of Music Opens at Rivoli |newspaper=The New York Times |date=March 3, 1965 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9804E4DF153CE733A25750C0A9659C946491D6CF |accessdate=February 27, 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150306053133/http://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9804E4DF153CE733A25750C0A9659C946491D6CF |archivedate=March 6, 2015 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"nytimes-singalong\">{{cite news |last=Vinciguerra |first=Thomas |title=Do You Really Call That Sound Music? |newspaper=The New York Times |date=August 20, 2000 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2000/08/20/weekinreview/do-you-really-call-that-sound-music.html |accessdate=January 27, 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/2015021005541